Interface WfwChannelData

All Known Subinterfaces:
FeedChannel, WfwChannel
All Known Implementing Classes:
FeedChannelImpl, WfwChannelImpl
public interface WfwChannelData
Marker interface for channel-level WFW (Well-Formed Web Comment API) data and properties. This interface currently serves as a placeholder for potential future WFW channel-level extensions.
